 this emerging blockchain-based social media platform including\nthe effectiveness of its design and the operation of the consensus protocols\nand the reward system.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 15 Apr 2019 20:05:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 2 Feb 2021 03:48:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-03"}
