entiate modified gravity MOND from modified inertia and give insights\ninto alternative ways to tackle some astrophysical and cosmological puzzles.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 15 Apr 2019 20:27:43 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 27 Aug 2019 22:06:16 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 23 Jun 2020 13:29:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-24"}
