 lifetime of the H$^2\\Delta$\nstate to 9.5 $\\mu$s.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 15 Apr 2019 20:46:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 9 Aug 2019 20:05:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-08-13"}
