rotron emission generated by the quasi-spherical\noutflow and off-axis top-hat jet increase as $F_\\nu\\propto t^{\\alpha}$ with\n$\\alpha\\lesssim 0.8$ and $\\alpha>3$, respectively. Finally, we obtain the\ncorrespondent SSC light curves which are in accordance with the\nvery-high-energy gamma-ray upper limits derived with the GeV - TeV\nobservatories.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 16 Apr 2019 14:38:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 5 Sep 2019 06:40:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-11-06"}
